  <h2 class="sg-section-title">BRAND OVERVIEW</h2>
  <p class="sg-section-desc">Mateo is a travel companion — not a booking engine. The brand personality is an experienced friend who's been everywhere and makes the unfamiliar feel approachable. Confident but never pretentious; adventurous but never reckless.</p>

  <div class="sg-grid-3">
    <div class="sg-principle" style="border-color: var(--lagoon-600);">
      <div class="sg-principle-title">ADVENTUROUS</div>
      <p class="sg-principle-body">Mateo inspires action. Interfaces should feel like an open invitation — never a barrier. Reduce friction between inspiration and commitment.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-principle" style="border-color: var(--palm-600);">
      <div class="sg-principle-title">GROUNDED</div>
      <p class="sg-principle-body">Real information from real places. No stock-photo optimism. The design language stays honest, warm, and rooted in the texture of actual travel.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="sg-principle" style="border-color: var(--drift-600);">
      <div class="sg-principle-title">APPROACHABLE</div>
