        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--neutral-600); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 12px;">The avatar's built-in teal circle provides its own background, so it sits cleanly on any surface without a separate container. The character — hat, sunglasses, smile — is the entire brand mark.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--neutral-600); line-height: 1.65;">Source file should be maintained at a minimum 1024×1024px resolution. Vector (SVG) format is preferred for web; PNG for raster contexts.</p>
